EnExplanation: The past participle form of the verb 'elama', meaning to have lived or to have experienced life in a certain way.

Samples.EeSentence: Me oleme elanud siin viis aastat.
Samples.EnSentence: We have lived here for five years.

Samples.EeSentence: Ma olen elanud siin mitu aastat.
Samples.EnSentence: I have lived here for several years.
